snippet.title: 3DO Gameplay: Immercenary
snippet.description:
Help support the channel: https://www.patreon.com/ZCInfinity

Fly through cyberspace, destroying the higher ranking avatars, until you're ready to take on the Perfect1 and shut down the cyberspace prison it's trapped all of humanity inside! ...Also, cyber-boobies.

Since this game is super-repetitive, I've edited most of it down to certain events happening, such as getting a rank, beating a boss character, or one of the many FMV sequences. Sorry for the choppy editing that resulted.
